sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as REST Client
    participant HTTP as rest-proxy HTTP Listener<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant JSON as CustomJSONPb<br/>Marshaler/Unmarshaler
    participant GW as grpc-gateway<br/>HTTP→gRPC Translation
    participant GRPC as gRPC Client
    participant MM as ModelMesh gRPC Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,MM: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (POST /v2/models/{name}/infer)
        Client->>HTTP: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Optional TLS
        HTTP->>JSON: Raw JSON request body
        Note over JSON: Decode nested tensor arrays<br/>Handle BYTES (base64)<br/>Parse InferParameter types
        JSON->>GW: Decoded ModelInferRequest protobuf
        GW->>GRPC: ModelInfer RPC call
        GRPC->>MM: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Optional TLS (localhost:8033)
        MM-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse
        GRPC-->>GW: gRPC response
        GW-->>JSON: ModelInferResponse protobuf
        Note over JSON: Marshal tensor outputs<br/>Encode RawOutputContents<br/>(little-endian + 4-byte delimiters)
        JSON-->>HTTP: JSON response body
        HTTP-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,MM: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request (GET /v2/models/{name})
        Client->>HTTP: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Optional TLS
        HTTP->>GW: Metadata request
        GW->>GRPC: ModelMetadata RPC call
        GRPC->>MM: gRPC ModelMetadata<br/>Optional TLS (localhost:8033)
        MM-->>GRPC: ModelMetadataResponse
        GRPC-->>GW: gRPC response
        GW-->>HTTP: JSON metadata
        HTTP-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response
    end
